_:N7a69d720b28c4d8790ddbc702a6f6cef <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Kate Dearden was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Department for Business and Trade on 7 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She was previously Assistant Whip, House of Commons between 18 July 2024 and 7 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Halifax in July 2024. She studied for <abbr title=\"Master of Arts\">MA</abbr> (Hons) International Relations at the University of Edinburgh and also previously worked for Community, a trade union.</p>\n\n" .
<https://www.gov.uk/> <http://schema.org/name> "Home" .
